&lt;/ul&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Spring Framework 6.2.17 and 7.0.6 Available Now]]></title><link>https://spring.io/blog/2026/03/13/spring-framework-6-2-17-and-7-0-6-available-now</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://spring.io/blog/2026/03/13/spring-framework-6-2-17-and-7-0-6-available-now</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[bclozel]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;On behalf of the team and everyone who has contributed, I am pleased to announce that Spring Framework &lt;code&gt;6.2.17&lt;/code&gt; and  &lt;code&gt;7.0.6&lt;/code&gt; are available now.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Spring Framework &lt;code&gt;6.2.17&lt;/code&gt; ships with &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/releases/tag/v6.2.17&quot;&gt;26 fixes and documentation improvements&lt;/a&gt;. This version will be shipped next week with Spring Boot &lt;code&gt;3.5.12&lt;/code&gt;.
Spring Framework &lt;code&gt;7.0.6&lt;/code&gt; ships with &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/releases/tag/v7.0.6&quot;&gt;45 fixes and documentation improvements&lt;/a&gt;. This version will be shipped next week with Spring Boot &lt;code&gt;4.0.4&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://spring.io/projects/spring-framework/&quot;&gt;Project Page&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework&quot;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/issues&quot;&gt;Issues&lt;/a&gt; | &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/reference/&quot;&gt;Documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item></channel></rss>